data.description: Start your next chapter at this beautiful custom home with panoramic Mission Mountain and Flathead Lake views, and a walking trail nearby! This 4BD/5BA 3,670 SF upgraded home sits on 0.5 acres and features 2 master suites, an oversized 3-car garage, and exquisite finishes throughout. The entertainer will love the built-in surround sound, covered patios, & lower level recreation room complete with a wet bar. Adjacent to the property is an 80-acre field owned by the HOA - ensuring unobstructed vistas. Upgrades include new custom luxury plank flooring, new thermostats, some new appliances, & updated kitchen cabinetry. Buyers have opportunity for 2.5% VA assumable loan.  Minutes to Flathead Lake, under 2 hours from Glacier National Park, Whitefish, and Missoula, making this the perfect middle point for Montana attractions. See Feature Sheet in docs. Call Jennifer Shelley at 406.249.8929 or your real estate professional.
